commit_message: Makefile should now work on OSX. Changed path to Boost library; also added -lboost_system to avoid undefined ref to system_category()

README includes background, install, usage instructions.
Main code includes checks for I/O parameters

More complete version of utility.
Added:
* README contains install/usage instructions, direction to example.
* An example dataset with script to run test
* A makefile
* A test script in the src/ directory
Initial write of mergePeaks_resolve.cpp. Successfully uses boost threads on a multi-core machine and resolves output of mergePeaks on H3K36me3 into a table of intensities.
